    {
      "para_id": "Q001078.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , Enlil’s warrior , En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , who makes the foreign lands submit to Ninĝirsu , child of Aya-kurgal , ruler of Lagaš , fashioned this vessel for crushing garlic , and dedicated it to Ninĝirsu for his well-being in the E-ninnu ."
    }
  ],
